"要将数据划分为不同类别，选择:guilabel:`Column grouping`、:guilabel:`Row grouping - First "
"level`或:guilabel:`Row grouping - Second level`下的字段。"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/studio/views.rst:327
msgid ""
